headline: Did Diamondback Energy's (FANG) Move Toward AI Power Shift Its Investment Narrative?
summary: In recent months, Diamondback Energy and other Texas oil and gas companies have begun pivoting toward powering AI-driven data centers as drilling activity in the Texas shale region slows and the state’s oil rig count reaches its lowest point in nearly four years. This shift highlights the intersection of energy supply and technology demand, with Diamondback adapting its business model to capture new opportunities arising from growing electricity needs in the AI sector.
